{"id":1620,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":385,"title":"Conversation 195","subtitle":"Restaurant Lunch Reservation","level":"B1","parts":16,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-195.1620/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/0-conversation-restaurant-reservation.mp3","transcript":"Hi there.\nI've arranged a meeting with some clients for lunch today.\nIt's under the name Samantha.\nOh, yes.\nI see your reservation.\nWelcome, Ms. Samantha.\nI know I requested to sit on your lovely terrace, but it's quite stuffy today.\nNo problem. I can seat you at a table inside.\nWould you mind waiting a moment?\nNot at all.\nBy the way, your parking lot is almost full.\nWhere should I tell my clients to park?\nOur guests can park at no charge in the lot behind the building.\nThe attendant will validate their parking tickets.\nThat's perfect.\nI'll call them now and inform them.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:03:09","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hi there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/1.mp3","time_start":0.53,"time_end":1.48},{"position":2,"content":"I've arranged a meeting with some clients for lunch today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/2.mp3","time_start":1.48,"time_end":5.0},{"position":3,"content":"It's under the name Samantha.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/3.mp3","time_start":5.0,"time_end":7.32},{"position":4,"content":"Oh, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/4.mp3","time_start":7.65,"time_end":8.89},{"position":5,"content":"I see your reservation.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/5.mp3","time_start":8.89,"time_end":10.55},{"position":6,"content":"Welcome, Ms. Samantha.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/6.mp3","time_start":10.55,"time_end":12.16},{"position":7,"content":"I know I requested to sit on your lovely terrace, but it's quite stuffy today.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/7.mp3","time_start":12.36,"time_end":17.16},{"position":8,"content":"No problem. I can seat you at a table inside.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/8.mp3","time_start":17.38,"time_end":20.72},{"position":9,"content":"Would you mind waiting a moment?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/9.mp3","time_start":20.72,"time_end":22.6},{"position":10,"content":"Not at all.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/10.mp3","time_start":22.89,"time_end":23.99},{"position":11,"content":"By the way, your parking lot is almost full.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/11.mp3","time_start":23.99,"time_end":26.77},{"position":12,"content":"Where should I tell my clients to park?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/12.mp3","time_start":26.77,"time_end":29.33},{"position":13,"content":"Our guests can park at no charge in the lot behind the building.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/13.mp3","time_start":29.55,"time_end":33.62},{"position":14,"content":"The attendant will validate their parking tickets.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/14.mp3","time_start":33.62,"time_end":36.86},{"position":15,"content":"That's perfect.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/15.mp3","time_start":36.86,"time_end":38.34},{"position":16,"content":"I'll call them now and inform them.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-restaurant-reservation-2024-09-30-22-58-45/16.mp3","time_start":38.34,"time_end":40.92}]}